00:33:04,610 --> 00:33:08,160
Other than my own feelings,

450
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:13,400
I should consider more for other people.

451
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:17,390
I should consider more for your sake.

452
00:33:17,930 --> 00:33:21,590
Silly.

