♫  The look of your happiness  ♫

457
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:53,110
Everyone, please sit.

458
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:04,450
Xueling, we can start.

459
00:34:04,450 --> 00:34:07,180
Today's meeting is mainly to discuss

460
00:34:07,180 --> 00:34:09,260
the design for the Symphony of Clouds and Mist Show.

461
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:12,070
The company views this show with high regard.

462
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:15,310
So we hope everyone will devote everything to this show.

463
00:34:15,310 --> 00:34:18,200
Right now, we have two designs in Cheng Yang's Water Colors

464
00:34:18,200 --> 00:34:20,130
and Liu Pei's Sunset Glow.

465
00:34:20,130 --> 00:34:22,840
Let's first ask Teacher Liu Pei to introduce

466
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:25,480
your design in the Sunset Glow series.

467
00:34:26,010 --> 00:34:27,790
After discussions, our team decided

468
00:34:27,790 --> 00:34:29,900
to use Danxia landform as the concept (various landscapes found in southeast, southwest, and northwest China that consist of a red bed characterized by steep cliffs)

469
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:32,260
which we will use for our design theme.

470
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:34,100
Please look, everyone.

471
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:38,260
Danxia landform has towering mountain peaks and deep precipitous canyons.

472
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:42,830
It is well-known for its red cliffs with rich color gradation.

473
00:34:42,830 --> 00:34:45,830
Therefore, in designing the color palette,

474
00:34:45,830 --> 00:34:48,360
we took inspiration from the Danxia landform.

475
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:51,290
The overall style of the clothing is western tailoring,

476
00:34:51,290 --> 00:34:54,160
using architectural style to showcase

477
00:34:54,160 --> 00:34:56,430
the mighty appearance of the mountains in Danxia landform.

478
00:34:56,430 --> 00:34:58,860
We then splice together different red colors

479
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:01,640
to present the layering effect in the overall clothing

480
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:05,130
and to reflect the Sunset Glow spectacle of rich colors.

481
00:35:05,130 --> 00:35:07,880
With this premise, we also use Su Embroidery

482
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:09,970
to embroider the lakes and rivers

483
00:35:09,970 --> 00:35:12,790
as beautiful embellishments.

484
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:21,850
Cheng Yang, what is the progress of your team?

485
00:35:23,950 --> 00:35:28,680
The theme of our team's design is called Water Colors.

486
00:35:28,680 --> 00:35:32,150
I hope, when people see this name,

487
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:35,030
they will relate to the classical elements in China.

488
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:37,290
The core design theme of Water Colors

489
00:35:37,290 --> 00:35:40,460
is a technique in Chinese brush painting: splash ink.

490
00:35:40,460 --> 00:35:42,980
We will use multiple dip-dying and splash ink

491
00:35:42,980 --> 00:35:45,910
to make our fabric just like we are painting.

492
00:35:45,910 --> 00:35:50,240
I hope that the fabric we present will show the scenery of clouds and mist,

493
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:54,930
clouds and mist turning into wind and rain, carefree and mystifying.

494
00:35:54,930 --> 00:35:58,920
What about the silhouette and tailoring? What are your thoughts?

495
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,650
For tailoring, we want to

496
00:36:01,650 --> 00:36:05,350
reference classical Chinese "Shen clothing" as the source of our inspiration. (A kind of clothing intertwined with the upper and lower garments of ancient times)

497
00:36:05,350 --> 00:36:08,240
Wouldn't "Shen clothing" be too thick and heavy?

498
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:12,530
We've considered that aspect. We will reserve some special characteristics of Shen clothing

499
00:36:12,530 --> 00:36:16,320
while considering modern people's clothing habits.

500
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:19,560
It will have the classic elegance and also present modern women's

501
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:21,400
curvacious figure.

502
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:25,470
It will simultaneously achieve youthfulness and lightness.

503
00:36:34,250 --> 00:36:37,020
Both teams have given us fantastic presentations today.

504
00:36:37,020 --> 00:36:40,890
After this morning, I am more confident

505
00:36:40,890 --> 00:36:42,980
with our Symphony of Clouds and Mist product launch.

506
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:47,520
Going forward, I hope everyone will work together

507
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:51,200
and elevate Minghuan Fashion to a better stage. Thank you.

508
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:58,220
Mingxuan.

509
00:37:01,310 --> 00:37:05,180
You were quite fair this time and did not favor Mo Fei.

510
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:09,110
You should know that I'm always fair and just.

511
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:11,240
I will not favor anyone.

512
00:37:11,240 --> 00:37:14,930
